⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Jimmy Woods
node WIZ · WIZ · ⟦Jimmy Woods:WIZ:b7ddaf⟧

WHO   — Jimmy Woods — 'The Wizard' — the near-mute prodigy
WHAT  — The film's heart: a traumatized savant whose only fluent language is the game, and whose one spoken word is 'California.'
WHERE — WIZ · The Wizard (1989)  Framework inputs: The Wizard (1989, dir. Todd Holland, Universal); verified cast & Nintendo history  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because he is the case for the game as a language — the boy who renders a grief he cannot say into a high score.
HOW   — By an uncanny mastery of any game put in front of him, and a silence broken only at the very end.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I can't tell you what happened to my sister — but watch me play, and you'll know exactly how it feels.

